name: 3D Mr Honest Necklace
description:
Story: Mr Honest was inspired by the tale of young Pinocchio. Our Mr Honest never lies, but guides us stylishly in the right direction. This charming puppet adores pretzels and has roots in Switzerland, which is why he wears the pretzel alpine forest hat inlaid with crystals. 

Mr Honest is a giggly chap with a witty sense of humour and a long gold plated nose (it doesn’t grow because he never lies!). His googly eyes are a window to his fun loving soul, and move around as you do. 

Product Details

- Necklace to wear long:  *24" (61cm)  *
- Gold plated chain necklace  
- Gold plated and enamel pendant  
- Engraved Go Jewellery message "HONESTY RULES" on the back of the pendant  
- Signature Go Jewellery red heart tag next to the clasp 
- Long protruding nose  
- Comical googly eyes
- Clear white sparkly crystals as salt crystals on Mr Honest’s pretzel adorned alpine hat

name: Mr Fox Badge Necklace
description:
Story: Get preppy! Mr Fox is Mr Honest’s mascot. This adorable fox has created his own coat of arms to reflect his principles in life and school of thoughts – his motto is ‘be trustworthy’.

Mr Fox’s coat of arms is engraved with his most precious beliefs on this school badge themed necklace:

1) Green Oak leaf – the noble strength of honesty 
 2) Mr Fox, who rests assured  
3) Purple and dark red stripes of tolerance and faith 

Mr Fox is completely content with the simple pleasures of life and the great company of Mr Honest.

Product Details

- Necklace length:  *18" (46cm)  *
- Gold plated necklace chain 
- Gold plated and enamel pendant  
- Engraved Go Jewellery message "REST ASSURED" on the back of the pendant  
- Signature Go Jewellery red heart tag next to the clasp

name: Lola and Burt First Class Bird 3D British Stamp Necklace
description:
Story: Lola and Burt are love birds. The entire world is connected online at the click of a button, overloaded by constant information in less than 140 characters. Our love birds are hopeless romantics, filled with nostalgia for a simpler time when we expressed our feelings with heartfelt love letters written by hand on beautiful stationary. It’s our love birds’ favourite way to communicate, and these extra special touches make falling in love that much easier. 

That’s why we’re portraying Lola and Burt in British Royal Mail First Class stamps. They’re no ordinary birds – simply First Class + adorkable.

The love birds have moon shaped eyes, heart wings, and cute bird bellies that protrude from the flat pendant. 

Product Details

- There are 2 colours for this product: Lola is red and Burt is blue.
- Necklace:  *18" (46cm)  *
- Gold plated necklace chain  
- Gold plated and enamel pendant  
- Engraved Go Jewellery message "FIRST CLASS BIRD" on the back of the pendant  
- Signature Go Jewellery red heart tag at the clasp
- Protruding bird (and cute belly) from flat stamp surface

name: San Francisco Lavender Peak Stud Geometric Necklace
description:
Story: The Peaks necklace collection was inspired by the diverse and fascinating cities we visited and fell in love with around the world. We have incredible memories from cities that motivated us to follow our ambitions and dreams to the highest peak. These peaks are represented by gold plated pyramid studs. 

San Francisco Lavender Peak Necklace – This quirky lavender coloured pendant was inspired by the city of San Francisco, where we spent memorable months and challenged ourselves to learn and develop in the Bay Area. We loved the diverse lifestyles and cultures we came across, from geeks and hippies to stylish fashionistas. 

San Francisco is represented by a gold plated pyramid stud on a lavender coloured gold plated and enamel pendant.

- Necklace length:  *18" (46cm)  *
- Gold plated necklace chain
